### About this documentation

This Copilot Space is designed to:
- Centralize project management knowledge
- Reduce onboarding friction and single-person dependency risk
- Enable rapid, consistent project delivery

For process updates, use the issue templates in `.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/`.
